***********************************************************************
*                                                                     *
*        THE HYPHENATION PACKAGE WHICH HAS BEEN IMBEDDED INTO         *
*        THIS VERSION OF 'SCRIPT' IS BASED ON THE 'HYPHENATION/360'   *
